<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们和帕克斯在车站的工作人员休息室里喝茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们自带了杯子，还带来一些饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯还是像平时一样，在啤酒罐里泡茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都很开心，说了很多话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帕克斯先生，您的生日是几月几号？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的生日？”帕克斯问，“我早就不过生日了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，您有出生的日子啊。”菲利斯思考着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十年前，或者六、七十年前！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没那么久，小姐！”帕克斯笑着回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其实，这个月15号我就32岁了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上孩子们商量了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯是他们最好的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他们决定为他的生日准备一些特别的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天吃早餐时，妈妈笑着给孩子们粥和牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我又卖了一个故事。”她说，“所以今天喝茶的时候会有面包。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯、鲍比和彼得互相看了看。他们在想同一件事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，我们可以改在15号吃面包吗？”鲍比问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那天是帕克斯的生日，我们想开一个小派对。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。”妈妈回答，“我们可以用糖粉把他的名字写在面包上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，鲍比说：“我觉得我们还需要一些花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我们需要有更多的想法！我们安静地想一想吧。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有了！”彼得突然大喊，“我想到了！”他跳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是什么？”女孩们着急地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帕克斯对每个人都很友好，一定有很多人想送他礼物。我们去问问大家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈说我们不应该向别人要东西。”鲍比有点犹豫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为了我们自己不可以，但是可以为了别人要。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他们出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邮局的老奶奶不想给帕克斯礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天是我的生日，但是没有人在乎。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为什么要在乎帕克斯的生日呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们离开邮局，去其他地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些人很友好，有些人不友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天过去了，彼得写下了所有收到的东西，就在他记火车车次的那个本子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>已收到的礼物：甜品店送的烟斗   商店送的茶</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>将会收到的礼物：肉店送的肉   农夫送的六个鸡蛋   铁匠送的铁锹</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，鲍比叫醒菲利斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们有一个彼得不知道的计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没告诉他是因为他可能会觉得很可笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们剪了一束玫瑰花，找到一张卡片，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并在卡片上写道：“兰塞姆女士，生日快乐！"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比和菲利斯带着玫瑰花和卡片来到邮局。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们在老奶奶进去之前，把东西放在了柜台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们到家时，彼得正在告诉妈妈他们要送给帕克斯生日礼物的计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那要看你们怎么送。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望他不会生气，觉得这是施舍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你要知道，穷人的自尊心是很强的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们这么做不是因为他穷。”菲利斯说，“是因为我们很喜欢他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>15号早上，孩子们看着妈妈用粉红色的糖粉装饰面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们去拿铁锹、鸡蛋和其他礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们经过邮局时遇到了老奶奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们的玫瑰花！”她说，“这是送给帕克斯的生日礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出一篮红醋栗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，我还有一个礼物给他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯一定会度过一个非常棒的生日！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>